{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"bd1d7816-2faf-4c1d-9b6b-c172446d5080","content":"Here's the recommended setup:\n\n## 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`) — minimal with MSTest.Sdk\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8.3\">\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` brings in the test framework, runner, and `Microsoft.Testing.Platform` automatically. No extra `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n## 2. Enable parallel execution globally\n\nAdd an assembly-level attribute (e.g. in a `Usings.cs` or `AssemblyInfo.cs`):\n\n```csharp\n[assembly: Parallelize(Scope = ExecutionScope.MethodLevel)]\n```\n\n`MethodLevel` runs all test methods in parallel (maximum throughput). Use `ClassLevel` if you want methods *within* a class to run sequentially but classes in parallel.\n\n## 3. Opt out for database tests\n\nDecorate your sequential test class with `[DoNotParallelize]`:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Inserts_And_Reads_Back() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Deletes_Existing_Row() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\nThese tests will run **after** all parallelizable tests finish, and will execute one at a time.\n\n### Key points\n\n| Concept | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| **Parallel by default** | `[assembly: Parallelize]` |\n| **Sequential opt-out** | `[DoNotParallelize]` on class or method |\n| **Granularity** | `ExecutionScope.MethodLevel` (max) or `ClassLevel` |\n| **Execution order** | Parallel tests run first, then sequential ones |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"f561f9b5-0791-4fd3-8d1d-d4c87169aee5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"No relevant files in the workspace. I'll provide the recommended setup based on my knowledge of MSTest.Sdk, parallel execution, and the `[DoNotParallelize]` attribute.","outputTokens":533,"requestId":"A02C:2086DF:654B555:6DD3664:6A034D74"},"id":"30642c39-3a43-4446-be25-45495814170e","timestamp":"2026-05-12T15:55:44.740Z","parentId":"85953bcd-d3a7-4c90-ad52-ba14f7038d00"}
